2015-08-20  Alec Leamas  <leamas.alec@gmail.com>

	lib: irrecord: Rewrite insane waitfordata loop.
	It is just an insane piece of looping. Besides, it doesn't
	work, and I don't care to finnd out exact why.

	New code does not loop for poll() errors besides EINTR. Better to
	break than to lock min such cases.

