	Merge branch 'merge-13' i. e. merge request #13.
	See http://sf.net/p/lirc/git/merge-requests/13.

	This branch makes the udp clock rate adjustable to better match
	modern hardware. It also includes fixes for the udp driver usage
	in mode2 and xmode2 + some enhanced docs.

	Kudos: Martin Tharby-Jones.

