2015-01-09  Alec Leamas  <leamas.alec@gmail.com>

	lib, plugins: Packaging noise: FSF addresses, git files, 644 scripts,

	lib: Remove offending exit() in libirrecord.

	irrecord-ui: Handle recent gcc compiler warnings.

