2015-01-09  Alec Leamas  <leamas.alec@gmail.com>

	Merge branch 'irr': Refactor irrecord into ui + library (#36)
	Splits the monolithic irrecord into a library (major part) + a
	CLI-based UI. The interface is based on return codes rather than
	callbacks, the usual solution for this kind of code. It's clumsy,
	but should work better when making language bindings.

	The library interface is experimental and not made visible in
	pkg-config etc. The API is likely to change substantially before
	0.9.3, and perhaps also after.

2015-01-09  Alec Leamas  <leamas.alec@gmail.com>

